snippet.title: Demo Trailer - Secret Agent Wizard Boy and the International Crime Syndicate
snippet.description:
Play the demo here!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3281870/Secret_Agent_Wizard_Boy_and_the_International_Crime_Syndicate_Demo/

This is the demo release trailer for my new game Secret Agent Wizard Boy and the International Crime Syndicate. Secret Agent Wizard Boy is a sandbox wizard sim that can be played alone or in cooperative(?) multiplayer. Explore (blow up) the castle, find secrets, solve puzzles, and discover the mystery hidden deep in the castle.
